{{italic title}} {{Taxobox | color = lightgrey | name = Acidipila rosea | image = | image_caption = | regnum = [[Bacteria]] | phylum = [[Acidobacteria]] | classis = [[Acidobacteria]] | ordo = [[Acidobacteriales]] | familia = [[Acidobacteriaceae]] | genus = ''[[Acidipila]]'' | species = '''''A. rosea''''' | binomial = ''Acidipila rosea'' | binomial_authority = Okamura et al. 2015<ref name="Acidipila-rosea">{{cite journal|last1=Parte|first1=A.C.|title=Acidipila|journal=www.bacterio.net|url=http://www.bacterio.net/acidipila.html}}</ref> | type_strain = AP8, KCTC 23427, NBRC 107607<ref>{{cite journal|title=Acidipila rosea|journal=www.uniprot.org|url=https://www.uniprot.org/taxonomy/768535}}</ref> | subdivision = | synonyms = }}
'''''Acidipila rosea''''' is a [[Gram-negative]], [[chemoorganotrophic]], [[acidophilic]] and non-motile bacterium from the genus of [[Acidipila]] which has been isolated from an [[acid mine drainage]].<ref name="Acidipila-rosea"/><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Okamura|first1=Keiko|last2=Kawai|first2=Akiko|last3=Yamada|first3=Takeshi|last4=Hiraishi|first4=Akira|title=Acidipila rosea gen. nov., sp. nov., an acidophilic chemoorganotrophic bacterium belonging to the phylum Acidobacteria|journal=FEMS Microbiology Letters|date=April 2011|volume=317|issue=2|pages=138–142|doi=10.1111/j.1574-6968.2011.02224.x|pmid=21255071}}</ref>
