{{Orphan|date=September 2018}}

'''Salma Al Kindi''' is an Omani chemist. She is professor of Analytical Chemistry and dean of the College of Sciences at the [[Sultan Qaboos University]] (SQU).<ref>[http://timesofoman.com/article/75301 Women excelling in research field in Oman, but face hurdles], ''Times of Oman'', January 11, 2016. Accessed March 4, 2018.</ref>

In 2017 she received a Lifetime Achievement in Chemistry Award from the Venus International Foundation based in [[Chennai]].<ref name="VIF">[http://www.muscatdaily.com/Archive/Oman/Lifetime-Achievement-Award-for-prof-Salma-al-Kindy-54oz Lifetime Achievement Award for Prof Salma Al Kindy], muscatdaily.com, Nov 1, 2017.</ref>

